<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.1.9">
<l>kiṭakkil toṭṭil kiḻiya vutaittiṭu</l>
<l>meṭuttuk koḷḷil maruṅkai yiṟuttiṭu</l>
<l>moṭukkip pulki lutarattē pāyntiṭu</l>
<l>miṭukki lāmaiyāl nāṉmelin tēṉṉaṅkāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [he] lays down, [he] kicks so that the cradle breaks.</l>
<l>If [he] is carried and held, [he] smashes the side of [my] body.</l>
<l>If [he] is subdued and embraced, [he] pounces on [my] belly.</l>
<l>Ladies! Because of being without strength, I have become weak.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
